<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The commited patch breaks connections to Oracle9i using the standard client.
It seems that the (PORT=nnnn) <em>MUST</em> be present otherwise, the client throws an "Invalid ADDRESS" error.</p>

<p>The workaround is trivial:
either specify the oracle port (1521 by default)</p>

<p>The proposed patch is also very simple, it just adds the port number.</p>

